sql:
SELECT SUM(quantity) AS total_quantity_ordered
FROM order_details
WHERE product_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
- "Treasure chest of categories" refers to product categories that have had multiple orders; 
- "Unlocked the door to multiple sales" means having more than one distinct order; 
- "Treasure accumulated" represents the total revenue for each category; 
- "Keys used to unlock the treasure chest" symbolize the distinct orders for each category.

sql:
SELECT AVG(rating) AS average_rating
FROM reviews
WHERE verified_purchase = 1;

external_knowledge:
- Top 3 implies the highest ranked 3 products; 
- Most reviewed implies the products with the highest review counts; 
- Safety Gear products refer to products that belong to the 'Safety Gear' category.
